<item>
            <title>[LU-2544] Add SMP scaling to Cray Gemini driver</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-2544</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Gemini LND driver for cray currently performs many task with some basic thread support but this driver does not total take advantage of the modern multicore systems that are present today in cray nodes. To improve the performance of this driver the SMP improvements of Lustre will be apply to the Gemini LND driver.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>Cray Gemini or Aries systems</environment>
